This project currently only supports Mac OS X --- a popular desktop operating system.

Mac OS X does not include a compiler toolchain (clang/gcc/make) by default.
This project uses these (and a Makefile) to build the project.  Please
download and install Xcode from the Mac App store to build this project.

Debugging

  Run "make gdb"

Running

  Run "make"

Cleaning

  Run either "make clean-fast" or "make clean"

Tests

  Run "make test"
